snippet.title: MTV's The Challenge
snippet.description: Following “The Challenge: War of the Worlds,” the lines have been drawn between the U.K. and the U.S. players.  Set in the middle of the jungle, “The Challenge: War of the Worlds II” returns to its classic team format; 14 Brits will battle it out against 14 Americans for their share of the $1 million-dollar prize.
